          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Building intelligent systems and predictive models for real-world applications.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-card p-6 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-700">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ðŸ“Š</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Data Engineering</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Designing and implementing scalable data pipelines and ETL processes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-card p-6 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-700">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">âš¡</div>
